import React from "react";
import {AppBar, Toolbar, Typography, Box} from "@material-ui/core";

function Navbar(){
    return (
        <>
            <Box mx={1} style={{ cursor: "pointer" }}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" color="inherit">
                                postagens
                            </Typography>
                        </Box>
                        <Box mx={1} style={{ cursor: "pointer" }}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" color="inherit">
                                temas
                            </Typography>
                        </Box>
                        <Box mx={1} style={{ cursor: "pointer" }}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" color="inherit">
                                cadastrar tema
                            </Typography>
                        </Box>
                        <Box mx={1} style={{ cursor: "pointer" }}>
                            <Typography variant="h6" color="inherit">
                                logout
                            </Typography>
                        </Box>
            
                    </>
    )
}

export default Navbar;
